{"tid":566304,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人在醫院隔離病房 求救","createTime":"2018-02-19T20:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T06:20:17.000Z","uid":156675,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d76a6fb9bde0da88e0dd2526d32613edff92de29","tid":566304,"uid":156675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:02:41.000Z","msg":"由年初一突然間急性扁桃腺發炎（白色珍珠果隻）<br />\n到尋日下晝初四前後睇左3次急症 last果次即是尋日下畫<br />\n頂唔順話要入院 因為十八歲果年都試過 好記得又是辛苦到入院三日先搞得掂<br />\n<br />\n由初一發炎果日起我已訓得好差 每次一訓低十秒八秒 左邊個鼻窿就會抖氣咁抖淡痰出黎 如是者不停咁重覆 我對上果48小時包括由我今晚7點到而家我是未撚訓到過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我初頭以為是扁桃腺發炎令到我個喉嚨窒左搞到呼吸唔順 到頭先果幾個鐘我試下靜心咁搵個問題出現係邊 就發覺我上面所講個問題 個感覺是個左鼻窿一抖氣條氣管就好唔舒服 好似氣促咁 一訓低事秒八秒淡痰就扯上黎責醒你 （右邊鼻無呢個問題）竟然巴打知唔知我咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我應該點同醫生講好<br />\n<br />\n我上網睇呢啲是咪叫肺積痰 我上月尾到月頭前後咳左好耐 飲左好多咳藥水 平時煙剷  <br />\n<br />\n今次真好是辛苦 立定決心戒煙多做運動 唔死過唔識驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ae64191213e793abc3899f337b65145d254b94","tid":566304,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:04:48.000Z","msg":"係咪有得去抽啖就無事"},{"pid":"04892edd9ddb69327c290471336930646dcba9e5","tid":566304,"uid":62952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:06:16.000Z","msg":"支持你戒煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝 身體健康"},{"pid":"9bdfe3c0bdbfb7d0029d73394f0c179a886ddf07","tid":566304,"uid":156675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ae64191213e793abc3899f337b65145d254b94","tid":566304,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:04:48.000Z","msg":"係咪有得去抽啖就無事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:10:54.000Z","msg":"我有試過係咁索啲痰出黎 索唔晒根本 醫生點抽我就唔知當然 我一索就係咁咳到死"},{"pid":"4f42c3f61d2b9ab123b8f731d7284665b3185ce7","tid":566304,"uid":156675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04892edd9ddb69327c290471336930646dcba9e5","tid":566304,"uid":62952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:06:16.000Z","msg":"支持你戒煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝 身體健康"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:12:13.000Z","msg":"多謝打巴 真心戒 呢獲最是人生最辛苦病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都祝其他巴打有決心戒煙"},{"pid":"ed73653039c023f76fe3627ac0079af0a2620cbb","tid":566304,"uid":62952,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支持你戒煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝 身體健康</blockquote>多謝打巴 真心戒 呢獲最是人生最辛苦病痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都祝其他巴打有決心戒煙</blockquote><br />\n我係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"120f32e6e4c9da4b010f3a76d2764db0272aff41","tid":566304,"uid":61206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bdfe3c0bdbfb7d0029d73394f0c179a886ddf07","tid":566304,"uid":156675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ae64191213e793abc3899f337b65145d254b94","tid":566304,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:04:48.000Z","msg":"係咪有得去抽啖就無事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:10:54.000Z","msg":"我有試過係咁索啲痰出黎 索唔晒根本 醫生點抽我就唔知當然 我一索就係咁咳到死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:18:00.000Z","msg":"抽痰好辛苦<br />\n要隊條喉入喉嚨吸"},{"pid":"7cb3bd510b7cf22e4b3e7047ba641c655ec41053","tid":566304,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120f32e6e4c9da4b010f3a76d2764db0272aff41","tid":566304,"uid":61206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bdfe3c0bdbfb7d0029d73394f0c179a886ddf07","tid":566304,"uid":156675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ae64191213e793abc3899f337b65145d254b94","tid":566304,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:04:48.000Z","msg":"係咪有得去抽啖就無事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:10:54.000Z","msg":"我有試過係咁索啲痰出黎 索唔晒根本 醫生點抽我就唔知當然 我一索就係咁咳到死"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:18:00.000Z","msg":"抽痰好辛苦<br />\n要隊條喉入喉嚨吸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:39:26.000Z","msg":"細個有次感冒左幾個月，<br />\n老母帶我去法國醫院睇下咩事，<br />\n個時個鼻太塞，就走去吸痰<br />\n其實無乜特別辛苦感覺，唔知係我太善忘定點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但係同時亦都唔知關唔關事地，我個鼻個嗅覺接近無左一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地個個話聞到死氣喉味漂白水味煤氣味我聞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲香水呀紅酒呀只要聞慣左陣味亦都唔會聞得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁多年黎都慣左所以無去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n樓主真係覺得有事/有好多痰既不妨搵醫生幫手吸吸啦，唔恐怖既<br />\n我個鼻應該都只係因為當年塞得太耐所以廢撚左姐，應該，好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f804d5e945110f5d3746945199bb80a4841e05","tid":566304,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:42:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪有得去抽啖就無事</blockquote>我有試過係咁索啲痰出黎 索唔晒根本 醫生點抽我就唔知當然 我一索就係咁咳到死</blockquote>抽痰好辛苦<br />\n要隊條喉入喉嚨吸</blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">細個有次感冒左幾個月，<br />\n老母帶我去法國醫院睇下咩事，<br />\n個時個鼻太塞，就走去吸痰<br />\n其實無乜特別辛苦感覺，唔知係我太善忘定點<br />\n<br />\n但係同時亦都唔知關唔關事地，我個鼻個嗅覺接近無左一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地個個話聞到死氣喉味漂白水味煤氣味我聞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲香水呀紅酒呀只要聞慣左陣味亦都唔會聞得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁多年黎都慣左所以無去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n樓主真係覺得有事/有好多痰既不妨搵醫生幫手吸吸啦，唔恐怖既<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">我個鼻應該都只係因為當年塞得太耐所以廢撚左姐，應該，好似係</span> </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉屌on lun 9明明睇到吸痰但以為吸鼻涕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自膠一打，返入老母個閪到先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81f3d42709db307866dd9ff1fd73909a035143e","tid":566304,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"屌我都想知 我又係食煙食到扁桃腺發炎跟住化膿<br />\n痛到仆街 結果都係要入廠 抽翻扁桃腺既膿出黎加訓左三日<br />\n但之後日日都仲係好多痰 日日喉嚨痛 個鼻同喉嚨好多痰可以互通咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之好撚煩 唉 真係後悔"},{"pid":"2a17a262172aa332532a3767b2f9b6cb28dffcc8","tid":566304,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:47:32.000Z","msg":"睇左好多次醫生 話係鼻敏感喎<br />\n係咪撚鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b85be4c9a6f9b931584c177757b327a0b142ad","tid":566304,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f81f3d42709db307866dd9ff1fd73909a035143e","tid":566304,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T20:45:47.000Z","msg":"屌我都想知 我又係食煙食到扁桃腺發炎跟住化膿<br />\n痛到仆街 結果都係要入廠 抽翻扁桃腺既膿出黎加訓左三日<br />\n但之後日日都仲係好多痰 日日喉嚨痛 個鼻同喉嚨好多痰可以互通咁<img src=\"/assets/fa